{"tid":121450,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"機皇EOS M3後繼機－Canon EOS M6 正式發表！","createTime":"2017-02-15T09:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T07:21:36.000Z","uid":523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9561aa591e710b4e0d6293bfd27ae35e9f7b4e29","tid":121450,"uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.dcfever.com/articles/news/2017/02/170215_m6_08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2017%2F02%2F170215_m6_08.jpg&h=29356e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搶在 CP+ 開幕之前 Canon 終由於出手，一口氣便發表了兩部單反及一部全新無反，雖然新機於網上早已流出，但正式發表時仍是有相當驚喜，特別是當中無反 EOS M6，在早前盛傳 Canon 會扣起 Dual Pixel CMOS AF 之下，如今便有失而復得的感覺，本來賣點不多的新機，吸引度即時大為增加。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.dcfever.com/articles/news/2017/02/170215_m6_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2017%2F02%2F170215_m6_01.jpg&h=367a7545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.dcfever.com/articles/news/2017/02/170215_m6_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2017%2F02%2F170215_m6_02.jpg&h=b8f572a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定位在 EOS M5 之下於 EOS M3 之上，最新的 EOS M6 於機身的設計上，顯然有 EOS M3 的影子，而相比起內置 EVF 的 M5，M6 機身設計就更為輕巧，需要的話，用家亦可另購外置 EVF 電子取景 EVF-DC2 ，個人認為對於強調輕便的無反來說，使用上便更有彈性。M6 機背配備了一個 3 吋多角度 Touch LCD，除了 45&deg; 向下翻，亦支援 180&deg; 反芒自拍。講到操控方面，相機亦應不難滿足有要求的用家，除了拍攝模式轉盤及曝光補償轉盤，另外分別於機頂及機背就設有 3 個指令轉盤，比起定位略低的 M3，操作上應該會更靈活方便。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.dcfever.com/articles/news/2017/02/170215_m6_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2017%2F02%2F170215_m6_03.jpg&h=745f7238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.dcfever.com/articles/news/2017/02/170215_m6_07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2017%2F02%2F170215_m6_07.jpg&h=f0157cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.dcfever.com/articles/news/2017/02/170215_m6_05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2017%2F02%2F170215_m6_05.jpg&h=b2307bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於內涵上，M6 大至用上跟 M5 相同的配置，除了 2420 萬像 APS-C CMOS 配備了賣點之一的 Dual Pixel CMOS AF 技術，相機亦用上新一代的 DIGIC 7 影像處理器，兩者配合之下，追焦連拍最快已有 7fps，鎖定對焦之下，更可進一步提高至 9fps，速度跟 M5 看齊。拍片方面 M6 依然未有加入 4K，不過相機就如 M5 一樣，內置有 5 軸式的電子防震，而針對更有要求的用家，M6 亦支援 3.5mm 外接收音功能。Canon EOS M6 預計將於 4 月賣街，機身定價為 780 美元（約 HK$6,052），套裝連 EF-M 15-45mm f/3.5-6.3 IS STM 定價為 900 美元（約HK$6,984），套裝連 EF-M 18-150mm f/3.5-6.3 IS STM 定價為 1280 美元（約HK$9,932），至於 EVF 取景器 EVF-DC2 的定價則為 250 美元（約HK$1,940）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.dcfever.com/articles/news/2017/02/170215_m6_06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2017%2F02%2F170215_m6_06.jpg&h=3cbf7c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉自<a href=\"http://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=18571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fnews%2Freadnews.php%3Fid%3D18571&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=fb84f283\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=18571</a><br />\n<br />\n街價跌到$4500 應該幾有競爭力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612403a553d701f7db79151d1e2fa3274fa3dbd9","tid":121450,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"跌到三千先有競爭力"},{"pid":"b30d7591550c297956ee07049c367dd223539d69","tid":121450,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"根本係m5 閹evf, 反芒向上flip<br />\n乜撚野吸引力大增？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個編輯一係智障，一係打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5cc69227fa46031f5dc100c1324cfd49d7f23e","tid":121450,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:55:16.000Z","msg":"自動對焦點選擇:<br />\nM5 - 直覺式觸控對焦操控 (Touch and Drag AF)<br />\nM6 - 沒有<br />\n觀景器:<br />\nM5 - 0.39吋類型電子觀景器 (約236萬點)<br />\nM6 - 沒有<br />\n螢幕大小:<br />\nM5 - 3.2吋 (3:2)<br />\nM6 - <span style=\"color: red;\">3.0吋</span> (3:2)<br />\n螢幕點數:<br />\nM5 - 約1,620,000點<br />\nM6 - 約<span style=\"color: red;\">1,040,000</span>點<br />\n電池:<br />\nM5 - * 交流電供應可經由交流電轉接器ACK-E17提供(另購)<br />\nM6 - 沒有<br />\n電池拍攝數量:<br />\nM5 - 於23&deg;C: 約295張 (一般模式)、約420張 (ECO模式)<br />\nM6 - 於23&deg;C: 約295張 (一般模式)、約425張 (ECO模式)<br />\n短片拍攝時間:<br />\nM5 - 約1小時25分鐘 (於液晶螢幕)<br />\nM6 - 約2小時25分鐘 (於液晶螢幕) 無理由多咁多，可能有伏<br />\n重量:<br />\nM5 - 約427克 (CIPA測試標準); 約380克 (淨機身) <br />\nM6 - 約390克 (CIPA測試標準); 約343克 (淨機身)"},{"pid":"1f58aebdee78be85be01c3092dcdcf84be3175d1","tid":121450,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:01:36.000Z","msg":"我冇睇錯下話 m3 呢 d 伏機都叫機皇？"},{"pid":"2cad453f5c276de9de247f60c3e2398b3f4bd641","tid":121450,"uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本係m5 閹evf, 反芒向上flip<br />\n乜撚野吸引力大增？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個編輯一係智障，一係打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nm5 機身定價7k8 跌到5k6<br />\nm6 機身定價6k 跌到4k 打m43 啲入門機同a6000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d7f0b75429c64acef178dea456ca577a929051","tid":121450,"uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我冇睇錯下話 m3 呢 d 伏機都叫機皇？</blockquote><br />\n曲線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2eb35bd00ac8c5f86af669863bdead9899a30fb","tid":121450,"uid":20390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"比較有興趣想知77,800，80有乜分別，除左五稜鏡同五面鏡"},{"pid":"cf